statements: SELECT * FROM topographic_survey_data;
SELECT survey_id, survey_date, surveyor_name FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE survey_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT surveyor_name, location_id, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE surveyor_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT survey_id, survey_date, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE elevation > 1000;
SELECT location_id, survey_date, surveyor_name, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data ORDER BY survey_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE survey_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT surveyor_name, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE elevation > 100 ORDER BY surveyor_name ASC;
SELECT survey_id, survey_date, location_id FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE survey_date < '2022-01-01' ORDER BY survey_date DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_surveys FROM topographic_survey_data;
SELECT survey_id, location_id, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE location_id = 10 AND elevation BETWEEN 50 AND 200 ORDER BY elevation DESC, survey_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM topographic_survey_data;
SELECT id, point_name FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE elevation > 1000;
SELECT id, point_name, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data ORDER BY elevation DESC;
SELECT name, license_number FROM surveyors;
SELECT id, name, license_number FROM surveyors WHERE id = 3;
SELECT * FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE elevation > 100 ORDER BY point_name ASC;
SELECT point_name, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE id = 5;
SELECT id, point_name, elevation FROM topographic_survey_data WHERE elevation BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY elevation DESC, point_name ASC;
SELECT tsd.point_name, s.name AS surveyor_name FROM topographic_survey_data tsd JOIN surveyors s ON tsd.id = s.id WHERE tsd.elevation < 50 ORDER BY tsd.point_name DESC, s.name ASC;

SELECT s.name AS surveyor_name, tsd.point_name, tsd.elevation FROM surveyors s JOIN topographic_survey_data tsd ON s.id = tsd.id WHERE s.license_number = '123456' ORDER BY tsd.elevation DESC, s.name ASC;
SELECT * FROM TopographicSurveys;
SELECT survey_id, survey_name, survey_date FROM TopographicSurveys ORDER BY survey_date DESC;
SELECT survey_name, survey_date FROM TopographicSurveys WHERE survey_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT point_name, point_elevation FROM SurveyPoints WHERE point_elevation > 1000 ORDER BY point_elevation;
SELECT point_id, measurement_type, measurement_value FROM SurveyMeasurements WHERE measurement_type = 'temperature' ORDER BY measurement_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM TopographicSurveys ORDER BY survey_date DESC;
SELECT survey_name, survey_date FROM TopographicSurveys WHERE survey_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT survey_name, point_name, point_elevation FROM TopographicSurveys JOIN SurveyPoints ON TopographicSurveys.survey_id = SurveyPoints.survey_id;

SELECT survey_name, measurement_type, measurement_value FROM TopographicSurveys JOIN SurveyPoints ON TopographicSurveys.survey_id = SurveyPoints.survey_id JOIN SurveyMeasurements ON SurveyPoints.point_id = SurveyMeasurements.point_id WHERE measurement_value > 100;

SELECT survey_name, point_name, measurement_type, measurement_value FROM TopographicSurveys JOIN SurveyPoints ON TopographicSurveys.survey_id = SurveyPoints.survey_id JOIN SurveyMeasurements ON SurveyPoints.point_id = SurveyMeasurements.point_id ORDER BY survey_date ASC, measurement_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM SurveyPoints;
SELECT point_name, x_coordinate, y_coordinate FROM SurveyPoints WHERE z_coordinate > 0;
SELECT id, measurement_type, measurement_value FROM SurveyMeasurements WHERE measurement_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT boundary, name FROM AreasOfInterest WHERE id = 1;
SELECT report_name, surveyor_name, report_date FROM SurveyReports ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM SurveyPoints WHERE x_coordinate > 10 AND y_coordinate < 20 ORDER BY z_coordinate DESC;
SELECT point_name, x_coordinate, y_coordinate FROM SurveyPoints WHERE z_coordinate BETWEEN 5 AND 10 ORDER BY point_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM SurveyMeasurements WHERE measurement_type = 'Distance' AND measurement_value > 100 ORDER BY measurement_date DESC;
SELECT id, name FROM AreasOfInterest WHERE ST_Area(boundary) > 1000 ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT report_name, report_date, surveyor_name FROM SurveyReports WHERE feedback IS NOT NULL ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM SurveyData;
SELECT id, surveyor_name, survey_date FROM SurveyData WHERE elevation > 100;
SELECT surveyor_name, survey_date, elevation FROM SurveyData ORDER BY survey_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM SurveyPoints WHERE latitude < 40.0 AND longitude > -100.0;
SELECT surveyor_name, terrain_type FROM SurveyData WHERE terrain_type = 'Mountain';
SELECT * FROM SurveyData WHERE elevation > 100 ORDER BY survey_date DESC;
SELECT surveyor_name, survey_date, elevation FROM SurveyData WHERE terrain_type = 'mountain' ORDER BY survey_date ASC;
SELECT sp.point_id, sd.surveyor_name, sr.findings FROM SurveyPoints sp JOIN SurveyData sd ON sp.survey_id = sd.id JOIN SurveyReports sr ON sd.id = sr.survey_id WHERE sr.report_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT DISTINCT sd.surveyor_name, sd.survey_date, sp.latitude, sp.longitude FROM SurveyData sd JOIN SurveyPoints sp ON sd.id = sp.survey_id WHERE sd.terrain_type = 'forest';

SELECT sr.report_id, sd.surveyor_name, sd.survey_date, sr.findings, sp.latitude, sp.longitude FROM SurveyReports sr JOIN SurveyData sd ON sr.survey_id = sd.id JOIN SurveyPoints sp ON sd.id = sp.survey_id WHERE sp.point_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
